| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2020-0131 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: da8ae1b9-aea4-5d9f-bbbd-38cc9bb486e0"
